msgid "A beheaded corpse."
msgstr "斷頭的屍體。"

msgid "Saki's beheaded corpse lies here."
msgstr "沙紀斷頭的屍體躺在這裡。"

msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgid "That can't be..."
msgstr "這不是真的..."

msgid "How is this possible?"
msgstr "這怎麼可能？"

msgid "I just saw her a while ago..."
msgstr "我剛剛才看到她..."

msgid "I-I don't understand..."
msgstr "我-我不懂..."

msgid "A bloody corpse. The lower half is missing."
msgstr "滿身是血的屍體。下半身不見了。"

msgid "Juli's bloody corpse. Her lower half is missing."
msgstr "由里滿身是血的屍體。她的下半身不見了。"

msgid "I..."
msgstr "我..."

msgid "This is my fault..."
msgstr "都是我的錯..."

msgid "A bloody corpse."
msgstr "滿身是血的屍體。"

msgid "Kaya's bloody corpse."
msgstr "香耶滿身是血的屍體。"

msgid "Oh no no no no no..."
msgstr "喔不不不不..."

msgid "Oh my god."
msgstr "我的天哪。"

msgid "This can't be real... It's not real..."
msgstr "這不是真的...這不是真的..."

msgid "Right...?"
msgstr "對吧...？"

msgid "...The door..."
msgstr "...門..."

msgid "I can... leave...?"
msgstr "我可以...離開...？"

msgid "I can... go home...?"
msgstr "我可以...回家...？"

msgid "I don't want to die..."
msgstr "我不想死..."

msgid "Why not? Everybody should try it at least once."
msgstr "為什麼不？每個人都該試一次。"

msgid "Right."
msgstr "對了。"

msgid "...It doesn't light up..."
msgstr "...點不起來..."

msgid "It's as if this place isn't dark... it's just black..."
msgstr "感覺就像是這個地方不暗...而是全黑的..."

msgid "That's not going to help."
msgstr "這沒有用。"

msgid "Unfortunately, the door has no keyhole."
msgstr "不幸的是，這扇門沒有鑰匙孔。"

msgid "Blood."
msgstr "血。"

msgid "Blood puddles."
msgstr "血坑。"

msgid "There's no door here."
msgstr "這裡沒有門。"

msgid "I cant... go back..."
msgstr "我不能...回去..."

msgid "A welcoming door."
msgstr "讓人感到歡迎的門。"

msgid "It's locked."
msgstr "被鎖住了。"

msgid "I... have to..."
msgstr "我...必須..."

msgid "...get out..."
msgstr "...出去..."
